Package assignmenttests.classlevel.products.method

Class MethodTest

java.lang.Object
assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTestBase
assignmenttests.classlevel.products.method.MethodTest
All Implemented Interfaces:
assignmenttests.AssignmentTest, assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTest
public abstract class MethodTest extends assignmenttests.classlevel.ClassTestBase
Abstract class that serves as a base for testing methods within a class. It handles setup, execution, and validation of method tests.
